                }

                    if (this._zoneDelegate.handleError(this, error)) {
                        throw error;
                    }
                }

                    }

                    if (newZone === task.zone) {
                        throw Error(`can not reschedule task to ${this.name} which is descendants of the original zone ${task.zone.name}`);
                    }

                }
